<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="mention-n">mention <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'menʃn/    美 /'menʃn/  </p>
<p>[U] &amp; [C]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>提及；说到：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She <strong>made no mention of</strong> her mother’s illness.
她没有提到她母亲的病。</p></div></div>